HEADWORD: Terin
<hw>Te"rin</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F. <ets>tarin</ets>,
Prov. F. <ets>tairin</ets>, <ets>t⟦eacute⟧rin</ets>, probably from the
